Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:05.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:08.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:09.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, I'm super stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how often I taste it, \NMaria's cookin's still the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you ate way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have ya know, comedy's about stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer body's yer capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If ya don't eat well, \Nyou'll never get a laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever plan to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if you're done eating, get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya don't need to tell me. I'm leavin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, I do the whole \N"serious student" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.41,0:00:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makita! Kunieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm off to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,School, school! What an annoying girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, you'll also need to \Nget ready soon, or you'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! Isumi's still asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.59,0:00:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I neglect my guest \Nand go to school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, so that's \Nthe tack she's taking today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be rough having so many \Nreasons why you cannot go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.44,0:00:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you insist on trying \Nto make me go to school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I head off to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get to be with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:11.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:14.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:18.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:20.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who is there to support his \Nmistress in all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:22.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:27.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This is about a boy who fights \Nand puts his life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:30.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we had forgotten for some time \Nthat Nagi has a crush on Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:43.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:43.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:50.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:50.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:53.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:53.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:58.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:58.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:02.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:02.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:06.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:06.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:11.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:11.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:14.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:14.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:21.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:21.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:27.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:27.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:30.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:30.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:39.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:39.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:46.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:46.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:53.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:53.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to Hell in Cat-Ear Mode
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! Why is it that Hayate \Ncan't just... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...see how a girl feels about wanting \Nto be together as much as possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, he's so dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning! Cleaning! Oh, what fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must like to clean, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, which do you prefer? \NSomeone older or someone younger?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so, in other words, are you \Nreferring to my taste in women?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:44.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Nagi and Hayate's relationship \Nis based on a misunderstanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:48.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I should try to get a clear read \Non exactly how Hayate feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:49.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...that in terms of the romantic \Nplotline of this anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:54.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the flag has been set for the Maria ending?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say, I like \Nolder women, hands down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:04:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Younger girls are adorable, \Nbut they don't interest me romantically!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be responding \Nwith some disappointment to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:08.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly! I will be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me. \NWe can discuss this again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:26.38,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Attendance Chart
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Nagi's absent again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, that suspicious \Nperson in black the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear he's the Sanzenin \Nfamily's new butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only caught a glimpse of him, \Nbut he was a young boy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup. I thought he looked pretty manly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like that wasn't quite the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then here, let's go get another look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayate, would you mind \Ntrying this outfit on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I hate to point out the obvious, \Nbut that's a girl's outfit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's in your size.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I mean. \NWhy do I have to wear a girl's outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...? Because... \NI think it'd look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing this on a whim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, it's on a whim,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I don't come up \Nwith things for you to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't spend time together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit complaining and put this on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop! Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making me wear a sailor \Nuniform... You're awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, it looks very good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make me happy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Let me get my camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't take photos of me like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the harm in it? \NIt's in commemoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's there to commemorate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if the head \Nbutler sees me like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:42.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It was actually only a couple days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:46.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,that Hayate received instruction \Nfrom Klaus, the head butler,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:48.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,on how a butler was expected to behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.23,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Butlers must be manly!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butlers must be manly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a butler of the Sanzenin family,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must be a gentleman and behave \Nin a manly manner at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This being an era of equality \Nbetween men and women,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,manliness is sought after all the more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are incapable of such behavior,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will expect your immediate resignation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I had no idea Klaus had said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't afford \Nto be seen like this by Mr. Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mr. Klaus isn't the only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she saw me like this, \NI'd die of embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, what are we to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a bit problematic \Nif you were to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I was, wondering \Nwhat you two were up to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to find you doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't what it looks like! \NThe Miss forced me to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Hayate insisted \Nthat he wanted to try it on, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe that you have \Na taste for cross dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried \Nthat you got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, what a child you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought it would look good on Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, a sailor uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I'm a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This frilly one is sure \Nto look good on Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Maria, in that case, \Nhow about this skirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But won't a pink one be cuter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'd say red.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! This blue one \Nis a tempting choice, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:21.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! They're both \Ntotally in high school girl mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:22.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My purity is in jeopardy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maria, what do you think of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:27.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, it's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't walk around the residence \Ndressed in a sailor uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but you know, \NI need to work and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, quite commendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll just call this work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try this on, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrible... Doing this to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not even funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:08:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mr. Klaus sees me, \NI really will end up getting fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is right. It is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one feeling embarrassed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But well, you know, \Nit really looks good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so, too, don't you, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tama, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be an animal, but that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not something you can do in an anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's do it! \NSeriously, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You stupid idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weigh over 300 kilos! You'll kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:47.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain to you kids \Nat home watching this for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:51.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, this tiger called Tama \Nis capable of human speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.95,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:55.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't ask me why he can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Maria,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is Tama assaulting Hayate because \Nhe mistook Hayate for a cute female?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is he assaulting Hayate \Nfor being a cute boy? Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on which it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of changing the course \Nof Tama's future education...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But well, it looks like Hayate may end up \Ndying even as you're saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:15.53,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, where's the harm?! Just a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! That's enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn stupid tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! He dropped Tama with one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may look like a girl, but inside, \NI guess he's still Herculean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-At any rate, I need \Nto get changed as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mr. Klaus sees me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, such a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On days like this, \Nthere is no better pastime
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than to go around giving new \Nmeanings to the garden flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:48.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:51.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, never mind that! I have to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A degenerate trespassing \Nupon the Sanzenin estate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,He could hardly say, "It's Hayate."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When all else fails...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can escape from me \Non the grounds of this estate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! That's Klaus for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is keeping up with Hayate's speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:21.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is bad. He's going to \Ncatch up to me at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this, I have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but to hide my face with \Nthe ribbon and intercept him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! I can't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:31.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But in a moment of peril, \Na person's latent powers awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:33.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than rely on my eyes, \NI have to have faith in my mind's eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That just wasn't going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, you miscreant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's an old guy doing \Ngetting all excited?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mr. Klaus. I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take this chance to change into these.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I am the one who should apologize \Nfor getting carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, you are kind, Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so grateful to you, Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:24.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If you weren't here, Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him? \NGoing on and on about Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:26.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how should I thank you, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:28.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what might have happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, hurry up and get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:31.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll spread the photos I took earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That is too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was kidding! Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Nagi not only hired a new butler,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a new maid, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Sanzenin family for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's an awfully cute looking maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem busy, though, so shall we leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, lunch break will be over soon anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we really need \Nto attend out afternoon classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,How the three student council girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:06.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...were able to slip through \Nthe tight security of the Sanzenin estate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:09.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and get onto the grounds is a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who in the world was that sweet lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ever see her again, I would like \Nto convey my feelings to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate's misfortune was far from over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chubby perv! (Mucchiri sukebe)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was touch you. \N(Betsuni sawatta dake janai)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, hot, hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:40.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \NI wonder what Ayasaki's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owowow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I got shoved over by Tama. \NThen I got kicked by Mr. Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got injuries everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My! You seem to have \Nsuffered quite an ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi! What in the world are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, when I woke up, \NI found I had become lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the experience utterly wore me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must have been quite an ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Your horrible sense \Nof direction is hardcore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how many times \Nyou've been over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times, I get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sanzenin estate is a horrific labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go making it sound all scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. It's late already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stay the night again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be sure to let your family know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Isumi saw me \Ndressed like a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think about it, don't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get to bed and end the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:14:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to sleep yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, I have to lie next to Nagi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since she's too frightened \Nto fall asleep alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but with Isumi staying \Nthe night again today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are relieved of your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Maria, I had no idea \Nyou played billiards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well... If you'd like, \Nwould you care to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:22.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And this might be a good time \Nto have a quiet talk with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:26.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering this morning's question, \Ncould this really mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:28.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the Maria ending has been \Nflagged in the romantic storyline?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:31.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason why I suffered all \Nthat horrendous bad luck today
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:33.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,was to lead up to this \Nmoment of happiness at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:38.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate was to regret feeling so \Ngiddy in this way shortly later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Isumi and the Miss \Ncertainly are good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi is special to Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They met 8 years ago at a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are these scribbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not scribbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:15:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're manga that Nagi worked hard to draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manga, ya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is this Rikishiman-looking \Nguy the villain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my mascot character! Hernia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's this? Ancient Incan script?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Lethal Old Man Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever it is, \Nquit drawin' this stupid stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and come play with us a little outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never draw another manga again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what are you doing, \Nreading that without my permission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back! Haven't you gotten \Nenough laughs out of it already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens next in that manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it was really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was how they met.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Less than a minute after \Nthey met, the Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how the two became fast friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Isumi is amazing. To think \Nshe could understand that manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right about now, Nagi \Nis probably going on and on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about a story that only \Nthose two can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right then, the ultimate weapon \Nthat came out of Ayers Rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Infinite Ant Production \NDevice, begins operating!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The infinitely outpouring ants \Ngather the world's sugar supply
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and takes it to the great defeated \Nwarrior general underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the heroes engage \Nin a three-way battle across the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fighting for the sugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But well, that is a thought \Nthat makes me worry for the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Hayate, where did \Nyou learn to play billiards?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I used to work part time \Nat a billiard bar back in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:51.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right for a minor \Nto work at a billiard bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:52.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will set that question aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! If you'd like, we could make a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:17:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I meant that as a joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then what shall we bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, how about something like
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the loser does one thing, \Nwhatever the winner wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This anime still technically \Nbelongs to a genre
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that caters to adolescent boys, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what are you intending \Nto make me do, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing... really that bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Hayate, \Ndon't tell me you actually think
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you even have a 0.1 \Nchance of winning against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Incidentally, if I lose, \Nwhat are you going to make me do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Well, let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that your 155,823,975 \Nyen debt is an awkward amount?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:18:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gets kind of long to say, \N"155,823,975 yen."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think 200 million yen \Nis a lot easier to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Today was a terrible day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:08.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but considering this turn of events,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,is Maria the last boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:13.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! I can't lose this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:16.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,However, faced with \Nan overwhelming difference in skill,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:19.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate is helpless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, this is a stupid question,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I should end up losing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how am I to repay my debt \Nafter it becomes 200 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be impossible, \Nno matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just joking about making my \Ndebt 200 million yen if I lose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like someone who cracks jokes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a possible way \Nfor you to repay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing. \NPlease, go ahead. It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, r-right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:51.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! I have to \Nturn the tables somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, with regards to the \Nquick fix way to repay your debt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a bold move, \Nlike you marrying Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?! Marry the Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way, that shouldn't count...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no take-backs in a serious match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if I make this shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your debt will become 200 million yen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you will have to seduce Nagi in earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I could never marry the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you don't like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that is not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to marry the Miss and my debt \Nwere forgiven because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be as if I married \Nthe Miss for her money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, this is hypothetically \Nspeaking! Purely hypothetical!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way the Miss would \Never fall for someone like me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even if such an unlikely \Nthing should happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a human being, I would \Nnever lay a hand on a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, the Miss is \Nthe person who saved my life
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she is very dear to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could never do \Nsomething like that to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:07.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate is a truly good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:11.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, here I've been trying \Nto pry into his feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:15.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps this is a matter that should \Njust be left to the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I still have a chance to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations! You win, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, I can really ask you \Nto do anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:55.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Something borderline \Nto cater to the adolescent boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should do something \Nabout the demon at your back first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the perverted \Nlook on your face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, this was nothing really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listen to me, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever lay a hand on Maria, \NI'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:20.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! He's got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going, Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:28.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The last boss that capped \Noff the unfortunate day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:31.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...turned out to be the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Hayate, what was it \Nthat you actually wanted me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was hoping to be forgiven \Nfor the expensive coat that I ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My! Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:47.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we all know, \Nthe butler-in-debt is a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:51.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, he will fight you-know-who \Nfrom the science room!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:56.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Moshi boku no yume ga kimi no kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:56.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If my dreams have taken your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:22:02.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kizutsuke-tetara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:22:02.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And brought it pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:07.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sono omoi wa itsuka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:07.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, that anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.17,0:22:10.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boku ga morau yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.17,0:22:10.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take from you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:17.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Taisetsu na mono ni furue-nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:17.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While trembling over something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:23.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kakezuri-mawatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:23.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And madly dashing about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:28.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seou itami ni hibi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:28.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The hurt I bore made the days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:33.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Muimi ni sugita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:33.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Go by emptily
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:38.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oikaketa mama de oikosare-tsuzuke
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:38.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just chasing and continually being overtaken
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.49,0:22:43.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tohou ni kureru kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.49,0:22:43.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A wind who's lost its bearing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.61,0:22:48.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi no doko ni furetara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.61,0:22:48.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of you should I touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:54.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ii ka o sagashita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:54.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I sought it out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.09,0:22:59.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mamoritai yo kimi dake wa tsuyoku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.09,0:22:59.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You alone, I want to protect so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:04.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yokubou no wadachi kara touzakatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:04.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting away from the rut of desire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.43,0:23:10.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Itsuka subete te ni ireru sore ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.43,0:23:10.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, it will all be ours and that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:14.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi to boku no Proof
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:14.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is our proof, yours and mine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:24.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Namida mo zenbu azukeru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:24.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Even all my tears, I entrust to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:29.22,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.64,0:23:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This episode of "Hayate the Combat Butler" \Nwas yet another masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.94,0:23:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In recording, it wasn't colored \Nyet, so it's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine! By the time it's \Nactually broadcast, it will be!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, this is \Na great song, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It conveys my desire to...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned that in a previous episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got it already, so well, \Ntry this on or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What is with this outfit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.37,0:23:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you as your manly self, \Nbut I find this hard to give up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.88,0:23:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never be a bridegroom now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you, so don't you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:23:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.99,0:23:58.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:00.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:18.74,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.65,0:24:02.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I forgot my notebook at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:04.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.11,0:24:05.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go get it for you right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:07.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not that important...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.99,0:24:09.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:11.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.40,0:24:14.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Elohim, Essaim. \NMr. Cow, Mr. Cow! What is it, Mr. Frog?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.50,0:24:18.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hayate from the Sanzenins is \Nat that old school building?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.21,0:24:19.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,At the hour of three-eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.74,0:24:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elohim Essaim. \NMr. Cow, Mr. Cow! What is it, Mr. Frog?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.64,0:24:21.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,let's meet again in the world of three-eyes!
